The paper deals with image segmentation using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of pruning and quantization techniques to simplify the network, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the use of medical images, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
